  "title": "Technical Support Assistant (Basic $3000/ Workshop Tool Room/ West)⚒️",
  "description": "<p>✔️ Basic Salary: $2500 - $3000 + $35 Laundry Allowance + $6/day meal allowance<br>\n✔️ Mon to Fri: 8.00am - 5.10pm<br>\n✔️ Location : Pioneer (Company provided at multiple locations.)<br>\n✔️Permanent Role + AWS + VB + 14 AL + Medical Coverage</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Responsibilities</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct regular checks in the inventory system to ensure stock accuracy.</li>\n  <li>Perform routine repairs and maintenance of yard and workshop tools and equipment.</li>\n  <li>Maintain the tool room through 5S practices and proper housekeeping.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Min.</strong> Technical Certificates qualifications.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office (Words, Excel).</li>\n  <li>Possess Class 3 license &amp; forklift license will be added advantage.</li>\n  <li>Able to work overtime including weekends.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>☎ Call 6817-2691<br>\n✉ WhatsApp 9422-1220<br>\nEA License No: 15C7752<br>\nEA Personnel No: R22111807<br>\nEA Personnel Name: Yap Teng hui</p>",
